> 2. Click the channel name → **Edit Channel** → **Integrations** → **Webhooks**
> 3. Click **New Webhook**
> 4. Give it any placeholder name (e.g. "Agent 1") — the name is overridden at post time
> 5. Click **Copy Webhook URL** — it looks like `https://discord.com/api/webhooks/1234.../abcdef...`
> 6. Repeat for each webhook slot
